==Sample== The sample text is a reading of the first sentence of [[The North Wind and the Sun]]. The transcription is based on a recording of a 28-year-old female speaker of standard Slovak from Bratislava.{{sfnp|Hanulíková|Hamann|2010|p=373}}
===Phonemic transcription=== {{IPA|/ˈras sa ˈsɛvɛraːk a ˈsl̩nkɔ ˈɦaːdali {{!}} ˈktɔ z ɲix jɛ ˈsilɲɛjʃiː/}}
===Phonetic transcription=== {{IPA|[ˈras sa ˈsɛʋɛraːk a ˈsl̩ŋkɔ ˈɦaːdali {{!}} ˈktɔ z ɲiɣ jɛ ˈsilɲɛjʃiː]}}<ref>Based on the transcription in {{Harvcoltxt|Hanulíková|Hamann|2010|p=377}}. Some symbols were changed to keep the article consistent - see the [[Slovak phonology#Vowels|section above]].</ref>
===Orthographic version=== Raz sa severák a slnko hádali, kto z nich je silnejší.{{sfnp|Hanulíková|Hamann|2010|p=377}}
